INSERT INTO `category` (`id`, `name`, `image`, `description`, `highlight`, `ordering`) VALUES
(1, 'ADVENTURE', 'adventure.jpg', '', 0, 11),
(2, 'BEACH, SPA & RELAX', 'beach2.jpg', '<p>From the white, sandy beaches and islands of the south, to relaxing amongst the beautiful scenery of rainforests and natural parks, there is a time and a place to take it easy. Spa treatments are plentiful and wellness options are developing in Cambodia.</p>', 0, 9),
(3, 'CITY & SHORT BREAKS', 'city2.jpg', '<p>Designed for those short on time and also for long weekend breaks from other Asian destinations. Take in the city highlights which include temples and museums, markets and top restaurants. Make the most of your valuable time and experience the best of Cambodia.</p>', 0, 2),
(4, 'CULINARY', 'culinary3.jpg', '<p>Explore Cambodia''s develping food scene which varies from Royal Khmer cuisine to world class restaurants in Phnom Penh and Siem Reap. Street food can also be an adventure for some. Learn about the differences to other Asians cuisines as our tours take you for mouth-wathering experiences.</p>', 0, 6),
(5, 'FAMILY HOLIDAYS', 'Family.jpg', '', 0, 8),
(6, 'CYCLING', 'cycling3.jpg', '<p>Cycling in Cambodia is an ideal way to see the stunningly beautiful countryside, see local villages full of friendly faces waving at cyclists and also stay healthy during your tour. Cambodia is extremely flat so clycling around the temples of Angkor or multi day options are easily arranged.</p>', 0, 5),
(7, 'GAY TRAVEL', '', '', 0, NULL),
(8, 'GOLF & SPORT', 'golf3.jpg', '<p>Like much of Southeast Asia a round of golf can be incorporated into a leisure or business visit. Courses host international tournaments such as the Johnny Walker Cambodian Open and rounds can be played in Siem Reap and Phnom Penh.</p>', 0, 13),
(9, 'HISTORY & CULTURE', 'image80.jpg', '<p>Wondrous temples with ancient carvings tell stories of the Apsara Empire. Culturally there is a lot to see and do including meeting local artisans and observing classical dance that is being rejuvenated in today''s Cambodia. A dveloping modern arts and cultural scene offers new opportunities to showcase the country as a leading light in the region.</p>', 0, 1),
(10, 'HONEYMOON & ROMANCE', 'romance3.jpg', '<p>Watching sunset over Angkor Wat or relaxing on a gondola cruise around Angkor Thom moat can provide special romantic moments to celebrate a honeymoon or special anniversary. Relax together at the hotel pool or spa treatment for two. Cambodia has much to offer the romantic at heart.</p>', 0, 10),
(11, 'NATURE & WILDLIFE', 'nature3.jpg', '<p>Unspoilt virgin forest, cascading waterfalls, the majestic Mekong River and the largest freshwater lake in Southeast Asia provide a dramatic natural landscape in which to explore. Freshwater dolphins, wild elephants, gibbon spotting and a huge variety of birds and butterflies will not leave nature fans disappointed.</p>', 0, 3),
(12, 'RESPONSIBLE TOURISM', 'responsible3.jpg', '<p>Cambodia has plentiful options to spend your money in a way that benefits local communicties. Dinning in vocational restuarants, supporting local tourism projects and purchasing authentic souvenirs all help sustainable development in the country. Tours can be designed to include as many responsible acts as possible.</p>', 0, 4),
(13, 'RIVER CRUISE', 'cruise2.jpg', '<p>The ultimate way to relax is by cruising on the Mekong and Tonle Sap rivers. Sightseeing is gentle and you won''t need to unpack at a different hotel each day. Sit back, watch the river scenery of floating villages, fishing folk who lives on houseboats and splendid sunsets-the true feeling of Indochina. Options for difference price levels are available as you experience in the best way possible, on board a river cruise.</p>', 0, 12),
(14, 'TREKKING OR WALK', '', '', 0, NULL),
(15, 'LUXURY JOURNEYS', 'luxury2.jpg', '<p>Champagne breakfast, helicopter flights and exclusive dinners can provide some memorables travel experiences. Combined with world class hotels in many areas, Cambodia is becoming a destination where you can travel in style.</p>', 0, 7),
(16, 'INSPIRATION', '', '', 0, NULL),
(18, 'INTERACTION WITH LOCALS ', '', '', 0, NULL),
(19, 'OFF BEATEN PATHS', '', '', 0, NULL);

