 Heading"/>\n </w:LatentStyles>\n</xml><![endif]--> <!--[if gte mso 10]>\n<style>\n /* Style Definitions */\ntable.MsoNormalTable\n	{mso-style-name:"Table Normal";\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\n	mso-style-priority:99;\n	mso-style-parent:"";\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n	font-size:10.0pt;\n	font-family:"Times New Roman";\n	mso-bidi-language:KHM;}\n</style>\n<![endif]--> <!--StartFragment--> <!--EndFragment--></p>\n<p>Sofitel Phnom Penh Phokeethra is set on the bank of the Bassac River amongst pristine landscaped gardens. The airport can be reached in 30-45 minutes and tourist sites are only a short drive away.</p>', 'sofitel-LOCATION.jpg', '<p>All 201 rooms and suites are spacious and well-appointed with hardwood floors. The rooms present the French contemporary flair mixed with Cambodian architecture and provides all facilities to maximize the guests&rsquo; satisfaction.</p>', 'sofitel-rooms.jpg', '<p>The eight restaurants and bars offer a superb range of dining facilities, from all day dining at La Coupole to Italian, Chinese &amp; Japanese venues. Chocolat is the ideal place to drink a coffee whilst you watch exquisite chocolates being created.</p>', 'sofitel-dining.jpg', '<p>Two outdoor swimming pools, the full-service So Spa, a Sports Club and fully equipped gym offer the chance to relax or work out during your stay in Phnom Penh.</p>', 'sofitel-leisure.jpg', NULL, '', '', '', 'sofitel-hotel-phnom-penh'),
(2, 'Angkor Paradise Hotel', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Angkor Paradise Hotel features 169 well appointed, spacious rooms built around a large swimming pool. With a resort feel and well located near the centre of Siem Reap the tourist sites are only a short drive away.</span></p>', 'Overview_-_Swimming_Pool_at_Night_IMG_5583.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">An excellent value for money hotel with a large pool. Rooms are spacious and all with a balcony. Angkor Paradise has a relaxing feel and a good choice for families and groups. We recommend the pool view rooms.</span></p>', 'for_website.png', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Centrally located in Siem Reap City, Angkor Paradise Hotel is situated only a 10 minute walk to the famous Old Market, the lively Pub Street and the bustling Night Market, and 15 minute drive to the UNESCO World Heritage Site of Angkor Wat Temple or the airport.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: ''Verdana'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #666666; background: #F8F6F6; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;"><br /></span></p>', 'Location_-_Terrace_by_the_pool_2_RMS_6038_(2).jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">144 Deluxe rooms are located facing the city or the pool. One wing has a Club floor with Club Classic rooms. All rooms are well appointed with tea and coffee making facilities, minibar, electronic safety box, flat screen TV and complimentary Wi-Fi. Bathrooms have separate bathtubs and showers.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Room_-_Deluxe_Twin_2.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The Palm Restaurant serves authentic Khmer, Asian and Western cuisines. Breakfast is served buffet-style, with a la carte lunch and dinner menus. The restaurant is set mostly indoors but expands to a terrace for those who prefer to dine alfresco. A pool bar and a lobby lounge both serve drinks and snacks.</span></p>', 'Dining_-_Pool_Terrace.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The swimming pool is the ideal place to cool down after some temple touring. A fitness centre offers a large selection of gym equipment plus sauna and steam rooms. Massages are available poolside, in a VIP room or your very own guestroom.</span></p>', 'Leisure_-_Picnic_by_the_pool_1_RMS_6049.jpg', NULL, 'Paradise Hotel in Siem Reap', 'hotel, siem reap, paradise', 'As its name reveals, this is a true heaven in the city of Siem Reap', 'angkor-hotel-paradise'),
(3, 'Angkor Village Resort', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Only a short distance from the temples, Angkor Village Resort features wooden cottages, restaurants and a spa all set amongst lush tropical gardens and along a unique 200m&nbsp; river shaped swimming pool.</span></p>', 'Overview_-_Angkor_Village_-_4444174759_d3369a4a43_b.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">We love swimming in the pool that snakes around the resort. Also the relaxing gardens and traditional style wooden cottages make an attractive alternative to concrete hotels.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Angkor Village Resort is located a 5 minute drive from the centre of Siem Reap or about 15 minutes to the airport.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Location_-_4444392251_04d324a7e3_b.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Angkor Village Resort has 40 cottages, each with Park View (downstairs rooms with a large terrace and easy access to the pool) and Pool View (upstairs rooms with balconies offering views of the pools and gardens). All rooms display the best of Khmer decoration complemented by modern amenities.</span></p>', 'Room_-_6778855758_d299cea766_b.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">In a traditional open air setting surrounded by water and greenery, "Aaraama" invites guests to take a culinary journey through the region.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The elegant indoor air conditioned room, &ldquo;Le Jardin&rdquo; offers an intimate dining experience with inventive international gourmet cuisine with a Cambodian touch.</span></p>', 'Dining_-_6778812526_9a3d629beb_b.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The meandering swimming pool snakes its way 200m through the resort. Enjoy relaxing treatments at the Spa Village or learn about Khmer cuisine with a cookery class. The sister resort, Angkor Village Hotel is located opposite the Angkor Theatre where nightly Apsara shows can be enjoyed.</span></p>', 'Leisure-Resort_Pool.jpg', NULL, 'Angkor Village in Siem reap', 'village, angkor, hotel', 'One of the oldest institution in the city of Siem Reap, the one hotel that has inspired many afterward', 'angkor-village-resort-cambodia'),
(4, 'Lotus Blanc Resort', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Designed in a French colonial style, Lotus Blanc Resort offers a comfortable stay whilst in Siem Reap. With a tropical landscape and large swimming pool the hotel offers value for money in a quiet environment.</span></p>', 'Overview-Lotus_Resort-pool_night_shot.jpg', '<p style="text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">A very relaxing tropical garden and pool are the highlights of Lotus Blanc Resort. The rooms will be refurbished in summer 2014 which will make it a great, small hotel with a boutique and fresh feel.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Located a short distance from central Siem Reap, Lotus Blanc is only 10 minutes drive from the airport or 15 minutes from the main temple sites.</span></p>', 'Location_-_Lotus_Garden.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Lotus Blanc offers 103 spacious rooms and suites. All rooms provide a private balcony overlooking a tropical view of coconut trees or city view of Siem Reap. Amenities include cable TV, minibar, electronic safety box, tea/coffee making facilities and complimentary Wi-Fi.</span></p>', 'Room_deluxe-room.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Le Blanc, the main restaurant serves authentic Khmer cuisine and Western flavours and features an open kitchen allowing chefs to showcase their work. The outdoor terrace is a nice place for a romantic dinner. The bright and cheery Lemon Bar is located in the lobby whilst Coco Bar, next to the pool, provides drinks and a relaxing venue.</span></p>', 'Dinning_-_le-blanc-restaurant.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">The 25m rectangular swimming pool offers a tropical landscape surrounded by huge coconut trees. A well-equipped gym overlooks the garden. Spa treatment is based around traditional Khmer massage and body wraps.</span></p>\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">A lobby shop provides authentic &lsquo;made in Cambodia&rsquo; souvenirs. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Lotus-Leisure.jpg', NULL, 'Lotus Blanc in Siem reap', 'lotus, blanc, angkor', 'The Lotus Blanc, one remarkable establishment with a very creative concept.', 'hotel-lotus-blanc-cambodia');
INSERT INTO `hotel` (`id`, `name`, `city_id`, `description`, `image`, `review`, `review_image`, `location`, `location_image`, `rooms`, `rooms_image`, `dining`, `dining_image`, `leisure`, `leisure_image`, `ordering`, `meta_title`, `meta_keyword`, `meta_description`, `url`) VALUES
(5, 'Maison Polanka', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Maison Polanka&nbsp;is a collection of two unique Cambodian villas offering hotel services in spacious tropical gardens.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Set in the sprawling grounds of a family estate, the property hosts 5 luxury suites &amp; rooms, an open air pavilion for the restaurant and lounge and an infinity pool.</span></p>', 'Overview-maison3.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">A great place for larger family groups &ndash; possibly to take the whole property. Otherwise couples and long stay visitors will appreciate the privacy and first class service without the pretensions of a deluxe hotel. Maison Polanka is a true gem&hellip;an oasis of calm that feels like real Cambodia.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Located in a village area only 10 minutes away from the holy grounds of Angkor temples but still within walking or tuk tuk distance of Siem Reap town. The nearby temple, Wat Polanka adds to the authenticity.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Leisure_-_polankad11621.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The property hosts two unique Cambodian villas on stilts, the Maison and the Khmer House. The Maison provides 4 bedrooms and the Khmer House is 1 large suite with 2 levels. Both villas combine an interesting mix of art and traditional crafts with the comfort of modern luxury. The whole property can be rented as a private and exclusive residence.</span></p>', 'Room-kh7.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The concept of Maison Polanka is to allow guests to enjoy breakfast at any time of the morning, lunch in the afternoon and an intimate candle lit dinner in the evening. Take time to enjoy these private and unique moments with fine Khmer cuisine.</span></p>', 'Dining-cuisine1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Relax at the infinity swimming pool or pedal</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">into town on a Maison Polanka vintage leather-seat bicycle. Return to sip a cup of fine English tea or drink a refreshing cocktail.</span></p>', 'Leisure-pool1.jpg', NULL, 'Maison Polanka', 'polanka', 'Very beautiful property ', 'hotel-maison-polanka-siem-reap'),
(6, 'Navutu Dreams Resort & Spa', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Navutu Dreams Resort &amp; Spa offers a unique tropical-Mediterranean chic design that sets itself apart from other boutique hotels in Siem Reap. The 28 room boutique resort is spread over a hectare of tropical gardens set in a quiet area just a few minutes drive outside of town.</span></p>', 'Overview-DSC_8833.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">A super relaxing resort ideal for couples, families, wellness fans and anyone with time to chill at one of the three pools. This is the sort of place where having a morning tour and the afternoon to relax at the pool, or getting a massage, just go hand in hand.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Located in the countryside but less than 10 minutes from the centre of town, Navutu Dreams Resort &amp; Spa is spread over a hectare of tropical gardens in a quiet area. A resort tuk tuk provides transfers to Siem Reap town if required.</span></p>', 'Location-Sports_pool_and_Grand_Tour_Rooms.jpg', '<p class="Default"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Navutu provide 28 spacious and beautifully decorated rooms in 8 separate pavilion spread amongst the tropical garden. 18 spacious Explorer rooms have a terrace f