ily: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">.</span></p>', 'Room-explorer_interior.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">The open air fine-dining, Niam Niam Restaurant blends southern Cambodian flavours from Kep Province, Italian traditional recipes, international contemporary cuisine, and lovingly created vegetarian dishes.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Dining-DSC_4287.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">3 swimming pools offer something for everyone &ndash; two are lagoon style salt water pools and the other an 18m lap pool. A kids pool will also please the youngster. Navutu offers Cambodia&rsquo;s most complete yoga and fitness programmes courtesy of a wellness expert recruited from the renowned Chiva Som in Thailand. The spa provides 5 treatment rooms.</span></p>', 'Leisure.jpg', 5, 'Navutu Resort Angkor', 'Navutu', 'Among the latest charming hotel in Siem Reap Angkor, was born the Navutu Resort. Praised by many and also the competitors ', 'navutu-resort-angkor-cambodia'),
(7, 'Park Hyatt Siem Reap', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Park Hyatt Siem Reap brings luxury and charm to the heart of Siem Reap.&nbsp; 108 rooms and suites are encased in an elegant, contemporary, residential facade that dramatically rises above Siem Reap&rsquo;s skyline, and secluded by manicured gardens from public view.</span></p>', 'Overview-Park_Hyatt_Siem_Reap_7_(The_Courtyard_Garden).jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">We enjoyed an indulgent breakfast at Park Hyatt and also a few happy hours drinks in The Living Room. It&rsquo;s not just about eating and drinking &ndash; the rooms and staff are both superb. Also it&rsquo;s a very short walk to restaurants and bars so the location is ideal to shop and eat in the town.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Siem Reap&rsquo;s most centrally located hotel, Park Hyatt Siem Reap is within two blocks walking distance to the Old French Quarters &amp; Pub Street and equally fifteen minutes from Siem Reap airport and the Angkor Archaeological Park.</span></p>', 'Location-The_Courtyard_Garden.Evening_Shot_.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Khmer-inspired contemporary art and custom furniture create an exotic, resort-like ambience throughout the 108 rooms and suites. Guests will find Italian marble and dual vanities in the spacious bathrooms and in-room Nespresso coffee. &nbsp;The suites are some of the finest in the city with distinctive attributes such as private gardens and/or swimming pools.</span></p>', 'Room-krishna_PHSR-room1-new.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Cuisine of French and Indochine inspiration is a feature of the main restaurant, The Dining Room.&nbsp; In addition, the bar lounge, Living Room and the deli-patisserie, Glass House, feature comfort fare.&nbsp; &ldquo;Carefully sourced, thoughtfully served&rsquo; is the underlying philosophy behind each and every culinary journey Park Hyatt Siem Reap delivers.</span></p>', 'Dining-Dining_Swing.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Park Hyatt Siem Reap boasts two swimming pools: a salt-water lap pool made out of sandstone and a free-form garden pool. The spa offers six treatment rooms and a menu based on modern therapeutic concepts. The fitness centre features the latest cardiovascular and strength equipment.</span></p>', 'Leisure-krishnaphotoworks_parkhyatt-siemreap-(2).jpg', NULL, 'Hyatt hotel in Siem Reap', 'Hyatt Siem Reap', 'Formerly known as The Hotel de la Paix, erected in the mid 1900''s, the hotel in the city center is now a Hyatt hotel de la paix ', 'hotel-de-la-paix-hyatt-siem-reap'),
(8, 'Pavillon d''Orient', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Pavilion d''Orient is an colonial style boutique resort with touches of traditional Cambodian architecture. 35 rooms and suites are located in four mansions hidden in a lush tropical garden.</span></p>', 'Overview-Pavillon_dO_swimming_pool.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">An excellent boutique hotel with 2 swimming pools to choose from. Book early to avoid disappointment as Pavillon d&rsquo;Orient is rightly popular.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Pavillon d&rsquo;Orient is located in the east of Siem Reap town close to the popular local market, Psar Leu and on the road to the Small Circuit temples. It is about 15 minutes drive away from Angkor Wat and also the airport.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Location-Junior_suites_building_at_night.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">17 Deluxe rooms are located in two storey buildings overlooking the pool or gardens all with private balcony. 16 Junior Suites are larger with space with a convertible sofa/bed and all face the pool. 2 Junior Family Suites are ideal for families of 4. All feature minibar, free Wi-Fi, tea/coffee facilities and safety boxes.</span></p>', 'Room-deluxe_queen_size.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The open air, Le Planteur Restaurant invites you to discover the unique taste of Cambodian food. European dishes and snacks are also available.</span></p>', 'Dining-le_Planteur_restaurant.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Two salt water swimming pools will refresh your senses after a hot day discovering the Angkor Temples. One is 12m long and located in the tropical garden, the other is a 16m infinity pool with a child&rsquo;s pool at one end. A spa offers guests a full range of massages and body treatments.</span></p>', 'Leisure-les_bains_dOrient_swimming_pool_b.jpg', NULL, 'La Pavillon d''Orient', 'pavillon orient, siem reap hotel', 'Stay in a small paradise with the charm of past flavours', 'hotel-pavillon-orient-cambodia'),
(9, 'Raffles Hotel Le Royal', 19, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Phnom Penh is graced with Le Royal, a colonial building which has been welcoming guests since 1929. The impeccably-restored rooms are joined by interconnecting wings set around a garden courtyard and swimming pools. The famed &lsquo;Elephant Bar&rsquo; and colonial lobby invite travelers to experience the rich history of the property.</span></p>', 'Overview_-_Raffles_Le_Royal_07_PP_Exterior_148-v2.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">For those wanting a touch of history with top class service it does not come any better than Raffles whilst in Phnom Penh. Enjoy a slow breakfast and relax at the pool in between sightseeing. Even if you don&rsquo;t stay at Raffles, visit for Happy Hour to try the signature Femme Fatale cocktail at Elephant Bar.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Located in the heart of Phnom Penh, only 30 minutes'' drive from&nbsp;Phnom Penh&nbsp;airport and within easy access of the city''s attractions such as the Royal Palace, Central Market and the Russian Market. Wat Phnom temple is a 5 minute walk from Raffles.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Location-RLR_-_Phnom_Penh_1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Dating from the 1920s and distinguished by its blend of Khmer, Art Deco and French colonial architecture.&nbsp; Raffles Hotel Le Royal&rsquo;s 170 rooms, suites and apartments are all in colonial style, with wooden floors and overhead fans, and recently refurbished using local artworks and fabrics.</span></p>', 'Room_-_Landmark_Room.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Enjoy fine dining at&nbsp;Restaurant Le Royal, serving Royal Cambodian Cuisine and modern French cuisine.&nbsp;Or try a sumptuous buffet and extensive a-la-carte menu featuring European and Asian cuisine Caf&eacute; Monivong. Relax in a sophisticated and charming atmosphere at the legendary Elephant Bar and try the house cocktails.</span></p>', 'Dining-RLR_-_Restaurant_Le_Royal_5.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The Raffles Spa offers relaxation and rejuvenation through a wide selection of services and facilities including treatment rooms, jacuzzi, fitness centre, sauna and steam room. Two outdoor swimming pools give you the chance to relax at the end of a days sightseeing. Raffles features several boutique shops with exclusive Khmer collections.</span></p>', 'Leisure-RLR_-_Pool_at_Night.jpg', 2, '', '', '', 'raffles-hotel-le-royal-hotel-siem-reap'),
(10, 'Shinta Mani Club', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Shinta Mani Club is an upscale boutique property, created by acclaimed architect Bill Bensley showcasing 39 contemporary designed rooms and public spaces in a Khmer inspired design. This exceptional property enjoys a tranquil and leafy setting within Siem Reap - just a 15 minute tuk tuk ride from the magnificent temples of Angkor Wat.</span></p>', 'Overview_-_Shinta_Mani_Club_untitled.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Small, personable and well located &ndash; Shinta Mani Club is an excellent boutique option for Siem Reap. The friendliest service in town courtesy of their hugely successful Foundation project that offers poorer Khmer the opportunity to train and get a sustainable future.&nbsp; The food as Kroya Restaurant is also some of the best in town.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Shinta Mani Club enjoys a quiet and leafy setting &ndash; 15 minutes tuk tuk ride from Angkor Wat. Guests can enjoy this peaceful oasis which is within walking distance to the Old market, the cafes and bars of the vibrant tourist trail, the nearby riverfront and the Royal Gardens. Shinta Mani Resort is located just across the road.</span></p>', 'Location_-_Shinta_Mani_Club_kroya_procession.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">All 39 Superior, Superior Poolside, Deluxe and Deluxe Living rooms offer comfortable and stylish accommodation with modern facilities. Rooms are equipped with twin or king sized beds and the terrazzo bathroom provides a rainforest shower.</span></p>', 'Room_-_untitled.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Kroya Restaurant blends international as well as local product, combining fresh ingredients, native herbs and spices to create innovative meals. Meals may be enjoyed indoors or outdoors on one of the Khmer swings. Enjoy the cool vibe of the open-air Bensley&rsquo;s Bar for cocktails and more.</span></p>', 'Dining_-_untitled.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">One spa suite, three double treatment rooms and an outdoor massage terrace provide a relaxing haven for the body and mind to unwind from jetlag and temple touring at Shinta Mani Spa. Relax at the grey-tiled infinity lap pool or use the larger pool at Shinta Mani Resort, located across the road.</span></p>', 'Leisure_-_untitled.jpg', 1, 'Shinta Mani Hotel in Angkor', 'Shinta Mani', 'Tastefully decorated with a well-balanced combination of modern and ancient artefacts, this property is a model  ', 'shinta-mani-club-hotel-angkor'),
(11, 'Shinta Mani Resort', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Shinta Mani Resort is a newly renovated Bill Bensley designed 63 room boutique property. A stay at Shinta Mani Resort assists the Shinta Mani Foundation to achieve its goal of creating a bright future for the people of Cambodia. A percentage of all guests daily room rate will be contributed to the Shinta Mani Foundation.</span></p>', 'Overview_-_Shinta_Mani_resort.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">A boutique small hotel that benefits from the Shinta Mani Foundation and their investment in Cambodia&rsquo;s future by training staff to be your hosts. Enjoy the top service and great food at Shinta Mani Resort.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Shinta Mani Resort enjoys a quiet and leafy setting &ndash; 15 minutes tuk tuk ride from Angkor Wat. Guests can enjoy this peaceful oasis which is within walking distance of the Old market, the cafes and bars of the vibrant tourist trail, the nearby riverfront and the Royal Gardens. Shinta Mani Club is located just across the road.</span></p>', 'Location_-_shinta_mani_-_resort4.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Each of the courtyard-style resort&rsquo;s 62 rooms &amp; 1 junior suite enjoy first floor balcony views or direct access to the swimming pool and flourishing tropical gardens. Rooms enjoy &ldquo;a Bensley twist&rdquo; including mirrored feature wall, custom designed iron bed and hand crafted light fittings.</span></p>', 'Room_-_resort-poolview.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Enjoy all day dining at Bai Tong and choose from International comfort food as well as Khmer street food. Bensley&rsquo;s Bar and Kroya Restaurant which are located directly opposite the Resort at the Shinta Mani Club are open to guests for their enjoyment.</span></p>', 'Dining_-_resort-restaurant.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The 21m long swimming pool is a relaxing place set amongst tropical gardens. Guests of the Shinta Mani Resort may access the spa at the nearby Shinta Mani Club.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Leisure_-_resort-restaurant.jpg', NULL, 'Shinta Mani Hotel & Resort', 'shinta mani hotel, siem reap', 'Shinta Mani Hotel & Resort is the natural resort extension for this great hotel chain in the region', 'shinta-mani-hotel-and-resort'),
(12, 'Sofitel Angkor Phokeethra Golf & Spa Resort', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US">Sofitel Angkor Phokeethra Golf &amp; Spa Resort is a luxury hotel situated in a 6-hectare, peaceful, garden sanctuary. With a picturesque lagoon, huge swimming pool, A So Spa and a range of restaurants and bars, the French colonial elegance of the hotel with a touch of Angkor will not disappoint.</span></p>', 'Overview_-_Panorama_1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A resort that is worth another day to indulge in some of the best spa treatment in Asia. All round the facilities, rooms and gastronomic offerings are a delight.&nbsp;</span>An he ideal choice for couples, honeymooners and families.</p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Sofitel Angkor Phokeethra Golf &amp; Spa Resort is located 5 minutes away from the center of Siem Reap and 10 minutes from the World Heritage site of Angkor Wat.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Location_-_Overview_-_Sofitel_Angkor_-_3123_wlfh_00_p_1024x728_(2).jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The luxurious accommodation combines timeless colonial style and elegance with modern comfort in 238 rooms, all tastefully decorated with period furniture, leather sofas, four-poster beds, classic ceiling fans and hardwood floors. Set in a peaceful garden sanctuary, each room offers inspiring views of the pool, gardens or lake.</span></p>', 'Room_-_DSC_3098.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Choose from moonlit Khmer dining overlooking the gardens from the Royal Court, all-day dining with the flavours of Asia and Europe at Citadel or the luxury and romance of Siem Reap in Mouhout''s Dream, an elegant French-Khmer restaurant.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">The Explorer&rsquo;s Tales Bar, a lobby lounge, is a popular meeting place for high-tea and evening drinks.</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Dining_DSC_3529.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Luxurious spa suites sooth your body after a day of exploring Angkor''s temples at</span><span lang="EN-US">So SPA with L&rsquo;Occitane. Or work out in a gym featuring the latest in fitness equipment. An abundantly sized swimming pool amidst tropical splendour also awaits - as does the championship golf course.</span></p>', 'Leisure_-_DSC_3245.jpg', NULL, 'Sofitel in Phnom Penh', 'sofitel, chain, phnom penh', 'The french touch when it comes to luxury hospitality.', 'sofitel-angkor-siem-reap'),
(13, 'Sokha Angkor Resort', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Experience authentic Cambodian hospitality at the Sokha&nbsp;Angkor Resort, with 276 guestrooms&nbsp;and suites decorated with a modern Khmer design. The hotel boasts some of the finest facilities and services in Siem Reap, from a beautiful salt water swimming pool surrounded by frangipani trees to stylish restaurants serving local and international cuisine.</span></p>', 'Overview-Panaroma_Pool_View.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Excellent location near the centre of Siem Reap. We recommend the Pool View rooms for a balcony with a view of the beautiful swimming pool. Sokha Angkor has a great range of dining venues including the best Japanese restaurant in Cambodia.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The resort is located in the heart of Siem Reap and is within walking distance to the Old Market and the Pub Street. Both Angkor Wat and the airport are approximately 10 minutes drive from Sokha Angkor Resort.</span></p>', 'Location-Sokha_Angkor_Resort-Front.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Sokha Angkor Resort offers 276 guestrooms and suites. All of the spacious rooms feature Cable TV, free Wi-Fi, minibar, safety box, tea and coffee making facilities plus separate shower and bathtub. Club Suites provide access to Club Floor privileges.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Room-Deluxe_POOLVIEW_Room_King_Hollywood_Bed.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">East meets West at the Lotus Restaurant which faces the hotel&rsquo;s&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''Century Gothic'', sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">pool and beautiful gardens. Le Chanthou adds some French colonial style whereas Takezono provides Japanese cuisine at its finest. A lobby caf&eacute; and Irish Pub (in high season) complete the broad range of dining and drinking options at Sokha Angkor Resort.</span></p>', 'Dining-SAR006_The_Lotus1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Pamper yourself at the beauty salon or Jasmine Spa, relax in the salt water swimming pool or take advantage of the sauna, steam, jacuzzi and fitness centre. A business centre is also on site at Sokha Angkor Resort.</span></p>', 'Leisure-Salt_Water_Swimming_Pool.jpg', NULL, '', '', '', 'sokha-angkor-resort-hotel'),
(14, 'Tara Angkor Hotel', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">An excellent base for visiting the Temples of Angkor, Tara Angkor Hotel provides 206 value for money rooms. All rooms are decorated in a contemporary style with attractive Khmer touches.</span></p>', 'Overview_-_Tara_Angkor_-_front-night-1.jpg.1024x0_.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The location is slightly out of town but tuk tuks are cheap to head out for nightlife. Tara Angkor offers 4 star service and rooms for an excellent value for money price.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Tara Angkor Hotel is situated only 6km from the World Heritage site of Angkor Wat, 15 minutes&rsquo; drive from Siem Reap Airport. Angkor National Museum is a few minutes&rsquo; walk away. By tuk tuk it is a short ride to the town centre.</span></p>', 'Location_-_Tara_Angkor_-_dome-courtyard-3.jpg.1024x0_.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The hotel has 206 stylish guestrooms and suites with a distinctive, contemporary style which successfully blends Khmer culture with understated elegance. Tara Angkor has 179 Superior rooms, 20 Deluxe rooms and 7 Suites. All rooms feature LCD TVs, free Wi-Fi, coffee/tea making facilities, minibar and electronic safe.</span></p>', 'Room_-_superior-king-6_jpg_1024x0.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Tong Tara Restaurant offers buffet breakfast with a combination of traditional Khmer and International Cuisine.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: ''Century Gothic'', sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;">Frangipani Restaurant named after a flower which can be seen through the hotel garden&rsquo;s, offers a choice of European as well as Asian delicacies. Lily Lounge is a nice place for pre-dinner cocktails or to relax after a day&rsquo;s touring.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Dining_-_tong-tara-1-2_jpg_1024x0.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Tara Angkor provides a fitness centre and sauna, swimming pool with jacuzzi and the Tara Spa offers a true spa experience through its holistic approach of achieving the perfect balance of the body, mind and spirit.&nbsp;The hotel also offers a cooking class to learn about Khmer cuisine.</span></p>', 'Leisure_-_swimming-pool-3_jpg_1024x0.jpg', NULL, 'Tara Hotel in Siem Reap', 'tara hotel', 'Among the first modern boutique hotel, located on the way to the temples. Very comfortable ', 'tara-angkor-hotel-cambodia'),
(15, 'Victoria Angkor Resort & Spa', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US">Victoria Angkor Resort &amp; Spa</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">provides a sense of serenity with&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">graceful colonial architecture designed to be in harmony with its natural surroundings and is situated in the heart of Siem Reap, opposite the Royal Park. All 120 rooms and 10 suites feature a private balcony facing the pool, tropical garden or the Royal Park.</span></p>', 'Overview-Victoria_Angkor_Resort_Spa.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A perennial favourite: Victoria offers a very relaxing stay for couples and families alike. We recommend to upgrade to a deluxe room so your balcony faces the pool. Don&rsquo;t hurry your breakfast as it&rsquo;s the best in Siem Reap. Please note that Victoria Angkor will be closed 1-30 June 2014 for some refurbishment work.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The resort is situated in the heart of Siem Reap, opposite the Royal Park. Located within close proximity to the Angkor Temples, the town of Siem Reap and only 7 km from the airport.</span></p>', 'Location-VAK_Terrace_and_Pool.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Featuring a Victorian touch, rooms and suites come with dark furnishings, all with private balcony facing the pool, tropical garden or the Royal Park. All feature TV, minibar, safety box, free Wi-Fi and a bathroom with bathtub. 10 individually decorated Colonial Suites offer more space and a balcony or veranda.</span></p>', 'VAK_Superior_Room.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">International, Asian and local Khmer dishes are served at the all day dining, L''Escale Restaurant, while Le Bistrot de Siem Reap presents modern French gastronomy, complemented by the finest wines. L''Explorateur Bar and Le Pool Deck feature both light meals, exquisite cocktails and refreshing beverages.</span></p>', 'Dining-VAK_Le_Bistrot_de_Siem_Reap.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">Surrounded by tropical garden, the hotel houses a magnificent outdoor saltwater pool with a spa tub. A childrens wading pool is at one side. Relaxing massages and body treatments are available at the Victoria Spa. For children 12 years and under, there is the Victoria Kid&rsquo;s Club with drawing, arts &amp; crafts and cooking activities.</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;"><br /></span></p>', 'Leisure-VAK_Massage.jpg', NULL, 'Victoria Angkor Hotel and Spa', 'victoria in siem reap', 'One of the most majestic hotel property near the Angkor Wat temples, made in the strict colonial art sensus', 'victoria-angkor-resort-hotel-and-spa'),
(27, 'HERITAGE SUITES HOTEL', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US">A small and intimate boutique property, Heritage Suites offers beautifully spacious suites nestled in tropical gardens. As Cambodia&rsquo;s only Relais Chateau property you can rely on quality, gourmet food and excellent service from the attentive staff. Heritage offers authenticity and tradition whilst providing modern facilities andalso being socially responsible.</span></p>', 'Overview-Facade_2.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">One of our favourite Siem Reap hotels: the staff are superb with many coming from the Sala Bai hospitality school which Heritage support closely. The rooms are some of the most spacious to be found in Siem Reap and the food amongst the very best. Heritage is very well suited for couples of all ages and families.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Heritage is located close in a small village in Siem Reap though only footsteps away from the river. The hotel is set 6km from the renowned Angkor temples and 15 minutes from Siem Reap airport. By tuk tuk it is a 4 minute ride to reach the Old Market, the National Museum and lively Pub Street.</span></p>', 'travel-asia-heritage.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">With 26 rooms and suites, Heritage is an intimate property decorated with a blend of Asian and art deco themes. All rooms have king size bed with free internet, minibar, safety box and espresso machines. The popular Bungalow Suites, offer 75 m&sup2; living area including a small garden with seating, an outdoor or indoor shower, a private steam room and an over-sized roll-top bathtub.</span></p>', 'Room-Bungalow_Suite_1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">With a proactive chef creating innovative Khmer dishes, with a touch of western cuisine, wining and dining is a highlight of any stay at Heritage. In high season weekly Khmer BBQ fondues can be enjoyed to the backdrop of a classic Apsara dance performance at the poolside. A jazz evening every Thursday night should not be missed.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Dining-Heritage_Suites_Hotel_-_Dining_room.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A stylish spa features one single and two couple''s treatment rooms and are equipped with&nbsp;steam baths,&nbsp;rain showers and over-sized bathtubs. At the heart of the property lays an intimate and pristine salt-water pool. A boutique shop offers a selection of handpicked Khmer handicraft, contemporary Cambodian sculptures,&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US">silk scarves and fabrics, all from reputed artisans and NGOs.</span></p>', 'Spa_Room.jpg', 4, 'Heritage Suites in Angkor', 'heritage suites', 'A hidden jewel. This is probably the most romantic property in the region. Honeymooners...pack your luggage  ', 'luxury-hotel-siem-reap-angkor'),
(16, '4 Rivers Floating Lodge', 14, '<p><span lang="EN-US">A unique property in Cambodia, 4 Rivers Floating Lodges consists of 12 overwater tents securely moored on a quiet stretch of the Tatai River, within the Cardamom Mountains. Access is by boat only to their pristine river location.&nbsp;</span></p>', '4_Rivers_Floating_Lodge-Overview.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Set in an idyllic location, 4 Rivers is a great place to relax at the end of an Asian adventure. For people seeking multiple hotel outlets such as restaurants, gyms etc to it would not be suitable. Just put your feet up, read a book, swim in the river (that&rsquo;s your swimming pool!), or take an excursion.</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">4 Rivers is located on a calm stretch of the river in the Cardamom Mountains. Access is from Tatai Bridge which is 20 minutes from Koh Kong City. It is approximately 5 hours drive to Phnom Penh or about the same to Bangkok when heading west. The Thai border is just 30 minutes away.</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>', '4_Rivers_Floating_Lodge-Location.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">12 overwater tents are moored either side of the 4 Rivers reception/restaurant. The tents are African safari style and of excellent quality. All have a private terrace facing the river with access to swim. The tents all tastefully decored with double/twin beds, a TV (DVDs free to hire but no channels) and en suite bathroom.&nbsp;</span></p>', '4_Rivers_Floating_Lodge-Room.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The restaurant serves a mixture of local Khmer food with western options. Vegetarians are also catered for. Fine wines are on hand to match the menus.&nbsp;</span></p>', '4_Rivers_Floating_Lodge-Dining.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">4 Rivers is about relaxing. Take an excursion to Tatai Waterfall, local fishing villages amongst the mangroves or deeper into the jungle. Kayaks are available to explore the river and of course swimming is an option directly from your tent terrace. Massage treatments are also available.</span></p>', '4_Rivers_Floating_Lodge-Leisure.jpg', 3, 'Eco Lodge', 'Eco lodging in Cambodia', 'The first of its kind, the Eco Lodge 4 Rivers is a unique property floating on a river in the middle of the jungle', '-eco-lodge-rivers-floating-hotel-cambodia');
INSERT INTO `hotel` (`id`, `name`, `city_id`, `description`, `image`, `review`, `review_image`, `location`, `location_image`, `rooms`, `rooms_image`, `dining`, `dining_image`, `leisure`, `leisure_image`, `ordering`, `meta_title`, `meta_keyword`, `meta_description`, `url`) VALUES
(17, 'Bambu Hotel', 7, '<p><span lang="EN-US">Bambu Hotel is a centrally located hotel in the city of Battambang. Offering 16 rooms the boutique hotel combines local Khmer and French colonial architecture whilst providing guests with maximum comfort and convenience.</span></p>', 'bambu-overview-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Our favourite in the central area of Battambang &ndash; a well-run, boutique hotel with a nice pool to cool down in. An alfresco breakfast next to the pool is a good way to start the day.</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Bambu Hotel is located on the east side of Sangke River approximately 10 minutes walk from the main market area of Battambang.</span></p>', 'bambu-location-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">All&nbsp;16 <a title="Hotel Rooms" href="http://www.bambuhotel.com/bambu-hotel-battambang/hotel-rooms/">rooms</a>&nbsp;have en suite bathrooms, air conditioning, flat screen cable TV, DVD player, iPod dock, mini bar, room safe and private terrace (ground floor - standard) or balcony (first floor - superior). Free Wi-Fi is provided throughout. The 4 Suites are located in the main building and all feature antique Khmer king size beds.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'bambu-room-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The Russey Restaurant Battambang, meaning bamboo in Cambodian, serves the best of local and international cuisine. Food and drink can be enjoyed in the elegant dining room or more informally on the terrace or at the bar.</span></p>', 'bambu-dining-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Bambu Hotel has a salt water swimming pool, available exclusively for house guests.</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'bambu-leisure-1.jpg', 6, 'Bambu Hotel in Battambang ', 'bambu hotel, battambang', 'Bambu is one of the pioneer boutique hotel in the Battambang region. One we recommend', 'battambang-hotel-bambu-cambodia'),
(18, 'Rajabori Villas', 15, '<p><span lang="EN-US">Rajabori Villas is a recreation of a typical Khmer village with 10 traditional wooden houses in an unspoilt part of Cambodia. Located on the Mekong island of Koh Trong, experience rural Cambodia staying in comfortable, characterful villas.</span></p>', 'Rajabori-overview-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Traditional style houses on a charming river island &ndash; not the sort of place for people who want Wi-Fi and Cable TV (they have neither) &ndash; with a super pool to relax. Definitely worth having a free afternoon during a tour to relax at Rajabori Villas. An excellent place to break the journey for a couple of days.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Rajabori Villas is located on the Mekong island of Koh Trong. Access is by road to Kratie town (4 hours from Phnom Penh) and then by boat transfer. From the Koh Trong pier a horsecart or moped provide access to Rajabori Villas. When the water level is high in rainy season a boat can arrive directly to the villas.</span></p>', 'Rajabori-location-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">10 traditional villas provide 10 rooms, all tastefully decorated with art and antiques collected from all over Cambodia. Rooms have a fan (no air-con) which is sufficient for the breezy Mekong island. All rooms have en suite bathrooms with showers. Some have bathtubs also.</span></p>', 'Rajabori-room-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The restaurant serves a mixture of local and Western dishes. A specialty of fish steamed in bamboo needs to be ordered in advance. A selection of wines is also available.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Rajabori-dining-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A large, outdoor swimming pool is located in the tropical gardens. Bicycles are available for Rajabori guests to explore the island. On Koh Trong visitors can take part in a plant a tree scheme to help the local community, see a Vietnamese floating village and visit the local temples.</span></p>', 'Rajabori-leisure-1.jpg', NULL, 'Rajabori Hotel & Villa in Kratie', 'kratie, hotel', 'Beautiful little villa hotel in the lost city of Kratie. A very good starting point for exploring the region ', 'rajabori-kratie-hotel-and-villas'),
(19, 'Maisons Wat Kor', 7, '<p><span lang="EN-US">Maisons Wat Kor is a 10 room boutique hotel located in the heart of a small beautiful village bearing the same name, located just outside of Battambang town. The traditional Khmer wooden houses on stilts are built around tropical gardens and the lotus pond.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'MAISONS_WAT_KOR-overview-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A delightful authentic Khmer property set in a real, unspoilt village. We recommend 2 nights here to soak up the atmosphere. The food is a real bonus &ndash; some of the best we have tasted at a small, boutique property.</span><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Maisons Wat Kor is two kilometres from the city center of Battambang, in the heritage visit of Wat Kor. A tuk tuk can provide transfers for visits into the town or for touring.</span></p>', 'MAISONS_WAT_KOR-location-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Maisons Wat Kor consists of 3 wooden houses containing 10 rooms. All rooms provide free Wi-Fi, minibar, safety box and tea/coffee making facilities. An LCD Cable TV is on request. The Frangipane rooms can connect making them an ideal option for families.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'MAISONS_WAT_KOR-room-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">La Terrasse de Lotus Restaurant and Bar faces the lotus pond and the tropical garden. Offering unique authentic Khmer food with some international dishes, daily specials are made with produce fresh from the garden and the local market.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'MAISONS_WAT_KOR-dining-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A salt water swimming pool offers the chance to relax after a days touring. Bicycles are available for rent to explore the local village and beyond. Several heritage buildings are within easy walking distance. Traditional Khmer massages are available on request. A demonstration of Khmer ingredients from the bio-garden can also be provided.</span></p>', 'MAISONS_WAT_KOR-leisure-1.jpg', NULL, 'Maison Wat Kor', 'hotel in Battambang', 'One of the latest addition to the boutique charming hotel of the colonial city of Battambang. A must see', 'hotel-battambang-cambodia'),
(20, 'The Frangipani Royal Palace Hotel & Spa', 19, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">The Frangipani Royal Palace Hotel &amp; Spa benefits from an excellent location just a couple of minutes walk from the river front area and the historic Royal Palace in downtown Phnom Penh. With a rooftop pool and restaurant, spa, and comfortable rooms, the hotel is the perfect base from which to explore Cambodia&rsquo;s capital.</span></p>', 'Frangipani-pnh-overview1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Rooms are a little uninspiring but this is made up for by the superb location and the rooftop pool overlooking the Royal Palace. We suggest an upgrade to the Balcony Suites rooms for an inspirational view. Begin your evening with a sake mojito at their rooftop bar before walking or taking a tuk tuk to the nearby riverside.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The contemporary Frangipani Royal Palace Hotel &amp; Spa is centrally located across from both the Royal Palace and National Museum on the edge of Phnom Penh&rsquo;s bustling art district. The airport is 30-45 minutes drive away.</span></p>', 'Frangipani-pnh-location1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The 72 rooms are furnished with locally made custom furniture in keeping with the architectural style of the hotel and all are air conditioned and have en suite bathrooms. Each room has a mini bar, free Wi-Fi, cable TV, tea and coffee making facilities.</span></p>', 'Frangipani-pnh-room1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The Royal Caf&eacute; serves buffet breakfast with a la carte lunch and dinner Khmer or Western options. The Royal Sky Lounge serves a similar menu but with views of the riverside from the 7th floor. The Royal Sky Bar offers excellent views over the river and the city and is the place to have a relaxing sunset drink.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Frangipani-pnh-dining1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The rooftop pool is the ideal to cool down after city touring with great views around the city. The Plumeria Spa offers a variety of revitalizing treatments.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Frangipani-pnh-leisure1.jpg', NULL, 'Frangipani Hotel & Spa', 'frangipani', 'Very cosy hotel and spa located in the heart of Siem Reap', 'frangipani-hotel-and-spa'),
(21, 'Himawari Hotel Apartments', 19, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Perched on the idyllic setting of Tonle Sap River, the Himawari Hotel Apartments enjoys splendid views of Mekong Delta in a tranquil resort haven. 115 suites and apartments combine with a range of leisure facilities to make a welcoming address for a stay in Phnom Penh.</span></p>', 'Himawari-overview-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Himawari benefits from having one of the best locations in town for touring. The rooms are spacious and a good option for families in Phnom Penh. Enjoy a glass of freshly brewed beer from the microbrewery at the end of the day whilst watching boats on the Mekong River from the gardens.&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The hotel is situated where the Tonle Sap, Tonle Bassac and Mekong Rivers converge in Phnom Penh and within walking distance of the Royal Palace, National Museum and the Riverside area of the city. The airport is 30-45 minutes away from Himawari.</span></p>', 'Himawari-location-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">All 115 spacious suites and apartments come with a comfortable sitting room and are ideal for in-room dining with a well-equipped kitchen. Amenities include Cable TV, DVD player, free Wi-Fi and safety box. Rooms offer panoramic views, some of the Mekong Delta and the Royal Palace.</span></p>', 'Himawari-room-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The Oyster Restaurant &amp; Bar offers fusion cuisine and twice a week, a popular seafood buffet. The Pool Caf&eacute; offers snacks and drinks with a fantastic view of Tonle Sap River. Biz Caf&eacute; serves a full range of selected coffees, teas and pastries. Himawari Hotel Apartments is the only hotel in Cambodia with its very own microbrewery.</span></p>', 'Himawari-dining-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">A swimming pool, fully-equipped gym and tennis court overlook the natural scenic beauty of the Mekong Delta. The Himawari Spa, offers a wide range of relaxing and rejuvenating treatments.</span></p>', 'Himawari-leisure-1.jpg', NULL, 'Himawari Hotel Phnom Penh', '', 'The Himawari hotel and apartments in Phnom Penh, on the riverside', 'himawari-apartments-holiday-rental'),
(22, 'La Maison d''Ambre', 19, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Located right in the heart of Phnom Penh, La Maison d&rsquo;Ambre offers 12 stylish, uniquely designed rooms. With an elegant white fa&ccedil;ade, typical of the Sangkum Era in Cambodia, the hotel offers rooms with individual art and design collected from the owners travels around the world.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'La_Maison_dAmbre(PNH)-Overview-photo-7.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">If you are looking for something different with an artistic, stylish touch then La Maison d&rsquo;Ambre is ideal. However as each room is different take a look at their website to book your preferred choice. The rooftop bar is a great sunset location. No swimming pool is the only minus point. Business travelers would appreciate as an alternative if they need to be based centrally.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">La Maison d&rsquo;Ambre is located centrally in Phnom Penh close to local markets, shops and just 2 minutes walk from Wat Phnom temple. Other sites of interest to tourists are within a short tuk tuk ride or even walking distance.</span></p>', 'La_Maison_dAmbre(PNH)-Location-bar3-francis.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Each of the 12 apartments is uniquely designed with Cable TV, DVD players, free Wi-Fi, safety box and a fully equipped kitchen. 3 One bedroom apartment are spacious at 60m&sup2;, all with king sized bed. 4 One Bedroom Plus offer additional space to relax and the 5 Two Bedroom room provide both king and twin beds with a balcony.</span></p>', 'La_Maison_dAmbre(PNH)-Room-china_14_robotang.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">With an almost 360 degree Phnom Penh view, enjoy Khmer and European food at the Fifth Element Restaurant &amp; Lounge.</span></p>', 'La_Maison_dAmbre(PNH)-Dining-bar_03_robotang.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">La Maison d&rsquo;Ambre can offer private masseur for in room massage. An excursion to the owners private countryside house by speedboat with the chance to enjoy a beautiful private swimming pool is also available.</span></p>', 'La_Maison_dAmbre(PNH)-moderne_14_robotang.jpg', NULL, 'La Maison d''Ambre in Phnom Penh', 'maison, Ambre, Cambodia', 'La Maison d''Ambre was erected after the famous couturier in Phnom Penh.', 'boutique-hotel-la-maison-ambre-phnom-penh'),
(23, 'Patio Hotel & Urban Resort', 19, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Patio Hotel &amp; Urban Resort is a recently opened, small hotel centrally located close to the tourist sites in Phnom Penh. The hotel features 45 rooms, a rooftop swimming pool, restaurant and bar.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Patio_Hotel_Urban_Resort(PNH)-Overview-.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The rooms are quite simply decorated. However nothing simple about the lovely infinity style swimming pool that offers some of the best panoramic views of Phnom Penh.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Patio is located within a few minutes walk of the Independence Monument, Wat Langka right in the heart of Phnom Penh. The airport is a 30-45 minute drive away. Numerous restaurants and bars are within easy walking distance of the hotel.</span></p>', 'Patio_Hotel_Urban_Resort(PNH)-Location-Lobby1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Superior rooms have twin or double options, some with step out balcony. All Deluxe rooms have balconies and are located on higher floors. A Patio Suite offers a large private balcony with excellent city view. All rooms come with minibar, Cable TV, safety box and Tea &amp; Coffee making facilities and en suite bathrooms.</span></p>', 'Patio_Hotel_Urban_Resort(PNH)-Room-Superior_Twin.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The 7th floor restaurant called &lsquo;Elephant in the Kitchen&rsquo; serves innovative Asian, European and Western dishes with an excellent viewpoint. The indoor bar or poolside bar offers chances to enjoy some cocktails and wines.</span></p>', 'Patio_Hotel_Urban_Resort(PNH)-Dining-Restaurant.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The 8th floor rooftop swimming pool is one of the best places to enjoy a cooling dip in Phnom Penh with superb city views. A business centre offers 3 computers to check emails. Massages are available at the massage centre or poolside.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Patio_Hotel_Urban_Resort(PNH)-Leisure-_TOF2233.jpg', NULL, 'The Patio - an urban resort', 'urban resort, phnom penh', 'Located in the residential district of the Capital, the Patio is a small jewel nested in a small alley', 'patio-hotel-and-urban-resort-phnom-penh'),
(24, 'Rambutan Resort', 19, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif'';">Rambutan Resort is a small, friendly boutique that focuses on privacy and friendly service. Located centrally, in a residential area, the hotel has a salt water pool with waterfall, pool-bar, restaurant and massage, all set within a tropical garden. Rambutan Resort is a gay friendly venture and is closely connected with the local community.</span></p>', 'Rambutan_Resort(PNH)-Overview-Swimming_Pool_6.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">You don&rsquo;t have to be gay to stay here &ndash; come with an open mind and enjoy the relaxed atmosphere and excellent pool.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: ''Comic Sans MS''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The resort is located in a quiet street just 5 minutes ride from many sights in Phnom Penh and in the middle of the centrally located residential area of BKK1. The airport is a 30-45 minute drive away.</span></p>', 'Rambutan_Resort(PNH)-Location-Standard_Garden_View_4.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Rambutan Resort consists of a city villa in Khmer style of the 1960&rsquo;s and a newly built modern designed wing overlooking a lovely pool. Standard Garden View rooms are located on the first floor of the old wing; the Deluxe pool view in the new wing and a top floor penthouse overlooking the city.</span></p>', 'Rambutan_Resort(PNH)-Room-Deluxe_Pool_View_2.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The Rambutan Restaurant serves both a wide variety of Western and Khmer favorites at its poolside location. A pool bar serves a variety of juices and cocktails. The culinary team consists of 3 young people who all studied at one of the qualified hospitality schools in Siem Reap.</span></p>', 'Rambutan_Resort(PNH)-Dining-Restaurant_2.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The resort has a salt water pool with waterfall, within a lush tropical garden. A spa offers health treatments such as aromatic oil massage, Japanese shiatsu massage by the blind, or the more traditional Khmer massage and even nail treatments.</span></p>', 'Rambutan_Resort(PNH)-Leisure-Swimming_Pool_3.jpg', NULL, 'Rambutan Hotel in Phnom Penh', 'gay-friendly hotel', 'The charm of the hotel, the hospitality of a gay-friendly property ', 'gay-friendly-rambutan-resort-cambodia'),
(25, 'Song Saa Private Island', 10, '<p><span lang="EN-US">Song Saa Private Island spans the islands of Koh Ouen and Koh Bong off the coast of Sihanoukville and are connected by a footbridge over a marine reserve established to safeguard the islands&rsquo; reefs and marine life. The 27 luxury villas are built using sustainable materials and all come with private pool.</span></p>', 'soongsaat-overview.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Some people might say this is too expensive but take a while to compare what is included against similar luxury resorts in Asia. Once you add in the full board, most drinks, lots of excursions and the speedboat transfers the cost is not as high as it first appears. An amazing exclusive hideaway that is worth the cost in our opinion.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">From Sihanoukville Port it is an easy 35 minutes to Song Saa Private Island on the luxurious resort speed boat.&nbsp;Daily flights provide access from Siem Reap to Sihanoukville. From Phnom Penh it is a 4 hour drive to Sihanoukville and then on by boat to the untouched Koh Rong Archipelago.</span></p>', 'soongsaat-locations.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Song Saa Private Island features 27 intimate villas, uncompromising on luxury and designed to reflect the simple beauty of the natural environment. Guests enjoy uninterrupted sunrise or sunset views from the Over-Water, Ocean-View and Jungle Villas, complete with private pools, and all the high-end creature comforts you could ask for.</span></p>', 'soongsaat-room.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">At the resort&rsquo;s heart is the Vista Bar and Restaurant, spectacularly surrounded by sea. Menus feature sustainably sourced local ingredients in a delicate fusion of traditional Khmer and Western cuisines. The rustic Driftwood Bar offers a pizza and tapas-style menu. Dine pool-side, in your villa or at a secluded hideaway spots for a private culinary experience.</span></p>', 'soongsaat-dining.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A large infinity swimming pool supplements the private pools of each villa with spa, yoga and meditation sanctuaries also provided. A range of leisure excursions including water sports and ecological programmes are part of the &lsquo;Song Saa Always-Included&rsquo; pricing policy with the only exceptions being motorised water activities, some adventure and conservation experiences as well as treatments at the resort&rsquo;s&nbsp;sanctuaries.</span></p>', 'soongsaat-leisure.jpg', NULL, 'Private Island off Cambodia', 'private island, Cambodia, perfect stay', 'Where can I rent a private island in south-east asia? Look here...its perfect', 'private-island-coast-of-cambodia'),
(26, 'Nita By Vo', 1, '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Nita by Vo, is a luxury 5 star boutique property designed by the acclaimed Cambodian architect, Hok. This recently opened hotel boasts of a rooftop pool ideal for sunset cocktails and 16 stylish rooms decorated with local arts.</span></p>', 'nita-overview-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">We really enjoyed our stay at Nita by Vo. Highly recommended for couples of all ages who want a touch of luxury but wish to avoid large hotels. Some of the best food you will find inside a small hotel including pies that are getting a good reputation amongst Siem Reap ex-pats.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Nita by Vo is located on Sivutha Boulevard and opposite Wat Thmey on the edge of the Angkor Wat Forest, 3km from the centre of Siem Reap town and 3km from Angkor Wat.</span></p>', 'nita-location-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">With large Internet TV&rsquo;s with DVD Player, minibar, room safe, free Wi-Fi, the 16 rooms are bright and sunny and most have balconies. All rooms have bathrooms with separate rain shower and double bathtub. The rooms feature in room art showcasing local student work that has captured the essence of the Khmer life.</span></p>', 'nita-room-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">The restaurant offers all day breakfast, Australian Pies and Western Cuisine with a Khmer tasting plate and western Cuisine evening. Fresh Baked Bread and specialty Pastries made on the premises. The Pool Bar and swim-up serves cocktails, beer, spirits and wine.</span></p>', 'nita-dining-1.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: ''Century Gothic'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Experience the healing power of Khmer ancient treatments and indulge yourself at Nita Spa. The rooftop pool offers view of Angkor Wat and is open 24 hours. A Lobby Shop sellsa wide selection of local handicrafts. A business centre offers a full range of services.</span></p>', 'nita-leisure-1.jpg', NULL, 'Hotel Nita by Vo', '', 'Hotel Nita by Vo in Siem Reap', 'nita-by-vo-hotel-siem-reap'),
(29, 'Terres Rouge Lodge', 33, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">Ideally situated on the edge of the Banlung lake, the Terres Rouge Lodge is a combination of a Cambodian villa and comfortable bungalows in the middle of an exotic garden. The lodge offers 29 rooms and suites and used to be the provincial governors former home.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Terres_Rouge_Overview.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The best available in Ratanakiri province with a lovely pool, nice rooms and most consistent service. Terres Rouges offers a boutique experience whilst in the provinces.</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Set on the edge of Banlung Lake, Terres Rouge Lodge is about 10 minutes walking distance to restaurants and bars in Ban Lung town.</span></p>', 'Terres_Rouge_Location.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">29 rooms and suites all vary in size and shape. Standard rooms are mostly fan only where Junior and Superior Suites provide TV&rsquo;s and all with air-con. The rooms, lounges and terraces are furnished with Cambodian antiques and objects manufactured by the twelve tribes of the province.</span></p>', 'Terres_Rouge_Room.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The bar-restaurant is located on the first floor and enjoys lovely lake views, best at sunset. The restaurant serves local specialties plus Khmer, Chinese and French fares. The bar offers a wide range of wine and spirits.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Terres_Rouge_Dining.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">A large swimming pool rewards tourists back from the tribal villages and treks and is flanked by a pool bar and Spa. Massages and body scrubs are also available. French guests in particular will enjoy the petanque court or bowling green. An on site boutique also sells local handicrafts. &nbsp;</span></p>', 'Terres_Rouge_Leisure.jpg', NULL, 'Hotel Terres Rouges in Cambodia', 'hotel in rattanakiri', 'One of the first pioneer hotel property in this part of Cambodia. It has well preserved all the essence of the natural surroundings', 'rattanakiri-hotel-terres-rouge-hotel'),
(30, 'Raffles Grand Hotel d''Angkor', 1, '<p class="MsoNormal">Raffles Grand Hotel d&rsquo;Angkor exudes old-world Cambodian grandeur infused with the best of modern comforts. Established in 1932, this grand and elegant hotel is spread over 15 acres of beautifully landscaped gardens and is the only authentic French Colonial hotel in Siem Reap. Raffles is the ideal venue for atmosphere, colonial charm, spa indulgence and gourmet dining.</p>', 'Raffles_Grand_Overview.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal">Classy with superb service. Relax and let the Raffles staff take care of your every whim. The pool is superb and even if you forget your suntan lotion the pool staff will have some on hand. Don&rsquo;t forget to try the Royal Khmer cuisine at Restaurant Le Grand for the ultimate dining experience in town.</p>', '', '<p class="MsoNormal">Set amongst 15 acres of serene grounds, the hotel is only 15 mins drive to both the airport and Angkor Wat. Overlooking the Royal gardens and directly opposite the Royal Palace, the Raffles is just a few minutes away from the vibrant markets and Pub Street area of Siem Reap.&nbsp;</p>', 'Raffles_Grand_Location.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal">Each of the 119 guestrooms and suites are tastefully appointed with Art Deco colonial style furnishings, blended with Cambodian objet d&rsquo;art reflecting the architectural theme of the period. Modern amenities are provided including minibar, in-room safe, free Wi-Fi and LCD flat screen TV and a round the clock butler service with signature Khmer hospitality.</p>', 'Raffles_Grand_Room.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal">Start the day with a champagne breakfast at Caf&eacute; d'' Angkor, relax at the Poolside Terrace during the day, sup afternoon tea at The Conservatory and fine dine with Royal Khmer cuisine at Restaurant Le Grand before evening drinks at the famous Elephant Bar. The Apsara Terrace also serves a sumptuous pan-Asian BBQ buffet as you watch traditional dances and Bokator martial arts.</p>', 'Raffles_Grand_Dining.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">Raffles offers the largest swimming pool in Cambodia &ndash; inspired both in design and size by the ancient bathing pools of the Khmer Kings in Angkor. The Amrita Spa provides a selection of massage and treatments. A fully equipped gym, sauna, jacuzzi and steam room&nbsp;</span>and two tennis courts offer ample opportunity to stay fit during a stay.</p>', 'Raffles_Grand_Leisure.jpg', NULL, 'Raffles Hotel in Siem Reap', 'raffles, siem reap, grand hotel', 'One of the most iconic property in the Angkor region, step back in time to the early explorer', 'hotel-raffles-grand-hotel-siem-reap'),
(31, 'PREAH VIHEAR BOUTIQUE HOTEL', 35, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">The 32 room Preah Vihear Boutique Hotel is located 27km from the UNESCO World Heritage temple and is the best hotel in the area. Rooms are tastefully decorated and built around a swimming pool.</span></p>', 'Preah_Vihear_Boutique_Hotel.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">Most people visiting the Preah Vihear temple will only spend one night in the nearby town. It is a pleasant surprise that Preah Vihear Boutique Hotel offers a comfortable stay. It won&rsquo;t be the most memorable hotel of a tour but more than meets the demands of a small provincial town.&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Preah Vihear Boutique Hotel is located in a quiet part of the small town of Sra Em (please note the actual &lsquo;Preah Vihear City&rsquo; is a further 80km away). The Preah Vihear Temple is located 27km from the hotel.</span></p>', 'Best_hotel_in_Preah_Vihear.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The hotel consists of 32 rooms which are built on two levels, the ground floor rooms have a garden terrace and first floor rooms a balcony. Rooms are tastefully decorated with the standard amenities, flat screen TV and a walk-in shower in the bathroom.</span></p>', 'Comfortable_rooms.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">On the first floor area above the reception the pleasant sitting area is split with a restaurant on one side and bar on the other. The menu has both Khmer and Western options. The hotel has its own bakery to produce the morning bread and pasties.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Restaurant_Preah_Vihear.jpg', '<p><span lang="EN-US">The saltwater swimming pool is a great place to cool down after visiting the temple. A children&rsquo;s playing area is to one side of the pool. Free Wi-Fi is available at the hotel. &nbsp;</span></p>', 'Saltwater_pool_Preah_Vihear.jpg', 29, 'Preah Vihear Hotel', '', 'Hotel near the Preah Vihear temple on the Cambodian side', 'hotel-in-preah-vihear-cambodia');

