ers of the Gulf of Thailand with a view of Bokor Mountain in the distance. Here you will learn several traditional fishing techniques, relax and enjoy a swim in shallow waters, or practice your own fishing techniques before gathering up the nets and heading back to the Sailing Club by boat.&nbsp; With luck, you may find that you have a selection of fish, shrimp, and crab to bring back. Large or small, the Knai Bang Chatt chef will be delighted to prepare your catch for you at the Sailing Club.</p>\n<p>After your return to the resort this afternoon the rest of the day is at evening. Why not relax with a spa treatment at Knai Bang Chatt or take a relaxing massage just metres from the sea?</p>', 'cambodia-cuisine-d9.jpg');
