hance to enjoy your own cooking for lunch&nbsp;<span lang="EN-US">(<em>cookery class may be shared with other participants</em>).</span></p>\n<p>The afternoon is free at leisure. Knai Bang Chatt offers plenty of leisure activities including mountain bikes for hire, tuk tuk tours or sailing courses. You can also take the chance to explore the local scenery &ndash; keep an eye out for the deserted and crumbling villas &ndash; relics of the 1960s when the French and rich Cambodians lived in the area. During the Khmer Rouge period many were evacuated and disused. Some of the villas have been restored though others are left in a state of disrepair.</p>\n<p>The evening is at leisure and we recommend some fine dining at the excellent Strand Restaurant of Knai Bang Chatt.</p>', 'cambodia-cuisine-d8.jpg');
